<subSubSection pageNumber="755" type="discussion">
<paragraph pageNumber="755">
<emphasis italics="true" pageNumber="755">
Note: 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Linnaeus" authorityYear="1753" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Polygalaceae" genus="Polygala" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fabales" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="heisteria">Polygala heisteria</taxonomicName>
</emphasis>
is homotypic with 
<taxonomicName authority="P. J. Bergius (1767)" authorityName="P. J. Bergius" authorityYear="1767" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Erythropalaceae" genus="Heisteria" kingdom="Plantae" order="Santalales" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="pungens">
<emphasis italics="true" pageNumber="755">Heisteria pungens</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation pageNumber="755" refId="references.r29">P.J. Bergius (1767)</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
, the 
<typeStatus>generitype</typeStatus>
of 
<taxonomicName authority="Linnaeus (1758)" authorityName="Linnaeus" authorityYear="1758" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Erythropalaceae" genus="Heisteria" kingdom="Plantae" order="Santalales" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageNumber="755">Heisteria</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation pageNumber="755" refId="references.r238">Linnaeus (1758)</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<emphasis italics="true" pageNumber="755">nom. rej</emphasis>
. in favour of 
<taxonomicName authority="Jacq. (1760)" authorityName="Jacq." authorityYear="1760" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Erythropalaceae" genus="Heisteria" kingdom="Plantae" order="Santalales" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageNumber="755">Heisteria</emphasis>
Jacq. (1760)
</taxonomicName>
(
<taxonomicName class="Magnoliopsida" family="Olacaceae" kingdom="Plantae" order="Santalales" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="family">Olacaceae</taxonomicName>
), 
<emphasis italics="true" pageNumber="755">nom. cons</emphasis>
. Levyns (in 
<emphasis italics="true" pageNumber="755">J. S. African Bot., Suppl</emphasis>
. 2: 216. 1954) indicated 882.33 (LINN) as 
<typeStatus>lectotype</typeStatus>
, but this collection lacks the relevant 
<emphasis italics="true" pageNumber="755">
<volumeTitle>Species Plantarum</volumeTitle>
</emphasis>
number (i.e. 
<normalizedToken originalValue="“13”">&quot;13&quot;</normalizedToken>
) and was a post-1753 addition to the herbarium, and is not original material for the name.
</paragraph>
